{"Data":{"Sdk":{"Events":[{"Id":"7806159646","Type":"IssuesEvent","CreatedAt":"2026-03-26T18:44:04","Actor":"alomakin-msft","Repository":"dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","Organization":"dotnet","RawContent":null,"RelatedAction":"opened","RelatedUrl":"https://github.com/dotnet/Open-XML-SDK/issues/2048","RelatedDescription":"Opened issue \"Feature request for Open XML SDK\" (#2048) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","RelatedBody":"**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\nWhen adding comments to openXML documents, it is necessary to use the CT_TextCharRangeMoniker (ISO/IEC29500-1:2016 2.29.3.23)  to highlight the text that is being commented on.\nExisting <ac:txMk elements will appear as OpenXmlUnknownElement\n\n\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\nOpenXML to include classes to construct the <ac:txMk and <ac:context items\n\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\nConstructing attributes manually\n\n**Additional context**\nNone"},{"Id":"7635870329","Type":"PullRequestEvent","CreatedAt":"2026-03-22T10:48:00","Actor":"SimonCropp","Repository":"dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","Organization":"dotnet","RawContent":null,"RelatedAction":"opened","RelatedUrl":null,"RelatedDescription":"Opened pull request \"\" (#2047) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","RelatedBody":null},{"Id":"7635723115","Type":"IssuesEvent","CreatedAt":"2026-03-22T10:31:59","Actor":"SimonCropp","Repository":"dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","Organization":"dotnet","RawContent":null,"RelatedAction":"opened","RelatedUrl":"https://github.com/dotnet/Open-XML-SDK/issues/2046","RelatedDescription":"Opened issue \"Consider dropping legacy frameworks\" (#2046) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","RelatedBody":"eg net35 has been out for 19 years. \n\nmy preference would be to have the min supported moved to 472. out for 8 years"},{"Id":"7635568632","Type":"PullRequestEvent","CreatedAt":"2026-03-22T10:15:19","Actor":"SimonCropp","Repository":"dotnet/Open-XML-SDK","Organization":"dotnet","RawContent":null,"RelatedAction":"opened","RelatedUrl":null,"